[
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "1",
    "Text": "When the sky splits open,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "2",
    "Text": "and when the stars fall away,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "3",
    "Text": "and when the seas burst forth,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "4",
    "Text": "and when the graves spill out,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "5",
    "Text": "&#761;then&#762; each soul will know what it has sent forth or left behind."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "6",
    "Text": "O humanity! What has emboldened you against your Lord, the Most Generous,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "7",
    "Text": "Who created you, fashioned you, and perfected your design,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "8",
    "Text": "moulding you in whatever form He willed?"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "9",
    "Text": "But no! In fact, you deny the &#761;final&#762; Judgment,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "10",
    "Text": "while you are certainly observed by vigilant,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "11",
    "Text": "honourable angels, recording &#761;everything&#762;."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "12",
    "Text": "They know whatever you do."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "13",
    "Text": "Indeed, the virtuous will be in bliss,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "14",
    "Text": "and the wicked will be in Hell,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "15",
    "Text": "burning in it on Judgment Day,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "16",
    "Text": "and they will have no escape from it."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "17",
    "Text": "What will make you realize what Judgment Day is?"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "18",
    "Text": "Again, what will make you realize what Judgment Day is?"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "82",
    "AyahNumber": "19",
    "Text": "&#761;It is&#762; the Day no soul will be of &#761;any&#762; benefit to another whatsoever, for all authority on that Day belongs to Allah &#761;entirely&#762;."
  }
]
